  npcName: Vendor
  npcPotrait: {fileID: 456460446371542513, guid: 52e5c4eb4a7baf6429ae1223cb064a72, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - "Tomatoes \u20B940 per kilo."
  - 'Transport cost up. Fuel up. '
  - Wholesale mandi rate up. Everything adds up.
  - Fresh vegetables are exempt.
  - "But crates, storage, transport \u2014 not exempt."
  - Input costs matter.
  - "For vegetables?  Most don\u2019t ask."
  - If I give full invoice, I report everything.
  - Then my turnover crosses threshold.
  - Then registration becomes mandatory.
  - Compliance increases. Filing returns every month.
  - "It\u2019s not about cheaper. It\u2019s about\u2014"
  - AVOIDANCE
